62.4	Mirror's_Edge	Mirror's Edge	Mirror's Edge is a single-player first person action-adventure video game developed by EA Digital Illusions CE (DICE) and published by Electronic Arts. The game was announced on July 10, 2007, and was released for the PlayStation 3 and Xbox 360 in November 2008. A Microsoft Windows version was released on January 13, 2009. Mirror's Edge is powered by the Unreal Engine 3 with the addition of a new lighting solution, developed by Illuminate Labs in association with DICE.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/9/97/Mirror%27s_Edge.jpg/250px-Mirror%27s_Edge.jpg
